    <h2>About ChatterBox</h2>
    <p>
        ChatterBox was developed as a solution for anyone who ever needed a private or public place to chat with individuals without distributing personal information or exposing themselves to other risks. It provides anonymous chatrooms to users at no cost with no sign-up required and is 100% ad-free. We only ask that you make sure to donate if you can so that we can continue to provide this service for the world! Happy chatting!
    </p>
    <p>A few things to get you started: If you're an administrator of a room, you can hit Delete while hovering over a user in the Participants list to kick them from the room. Remember that you'll have to log in as an administrator in the options menu. If you're looking to send a private message to someone, you can do that by simply clicking their name on Participants list.</p>
